Package: radxa-penta-fan-ctrl
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, smartmontools
Description: Fan control daemon for Penta SATA HAT top board
 This daemon monitors CPU and SSD temperatures and controls the fan
 speed and OLED display on the Penta SATA HAT top board accessory.
 Compatible with Raspberry Pi 4/5, ROCK Pi 4/5, and other supported boards.
 .
 Features:
  - Smart thermal control with hysteresis and trend analysis
  - Automatic fan speed control based on temperature
  - OLED display with system info, disk temps, and RAID status
  - Support for both hardware and software PWM
  - Configurable temperature thresholds and thermal tunables
  - SystemD service integration
